Package: yelpviz
Type: Package
Title: Wrap Yelp APIS for visualization of the interesting businesses in the specific area.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Nijiati Abulizi, Kulaphong Jitareerat, Craig Adlam
Maintainer: Nijiati Abulizi, Kulaphong Jitareerat, Craig Adlam
Description:
    The "yelpviz" package is designed to simplify the process of accessing Yelp APIs and 
    visualizing interesting businesses within a specific area. 
    Leveraging the power of Yelp's rich dataset, this package allows users to seamlessly retrieve business information 
    and create interactive visualizations to gain insights into local establishments.
Key Features:
    - Streamlined API Access: Easily access Yelp's API to fetch information about businesses, 
    including details like reviews, ratings, and location data.
    - Analyze Location: Provide a data frame, containing available businesses in an area and visualize them.
    - WordCloud Visualization: Visualize the Name businesses name as WordCloud.
    - Geospatial Visualization: Visualize the geographical distribution of businesses using interactive maps.
